Source: re2
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), g++, libre2-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/ClickHouse/pg_re2

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-re2
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-re2
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: ClickHouse-compatible RE2 regular expression functions for PostgreSQL
  re2 adds ClickHouse-style regular expression matching and extraction
  functions backed by Google's RE2 engine, providing linear-time regex
  behavior for PostgreSQL 16 through 18.
